data.description: $1500 Buyer Incentive*Convenient Tinseltown area of Southside, this luxury gated condominium community offers the convenience of being minutes to JTB, Publix, Restaurants & the Tinseltown Theater.*Gated community with pool, spa & fitness center*Experience the ultimate in privacy & security with secure parking & building entry. This condo is on the 2nd floor in building 5.  The elevator opens to each floor with its own elegant lobby with beautiful furnishings!  You are greeted by a tile entry foyer, separate dining room (big enough for a home office), fully equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances & granite counters.  You will love the inside laundry room with cabinetry & the washer & dryer stays!  Tile flooring in the foyer, dining room, kitchen & both bathrooms & wood flooring & carpeting in bedrooms.  The owner's suite has a garden tub, 2 sinks & huge closet.  Each condo has a private storage area*HVAC 4 years old per owners*$100 buyer transfer fee at closing*
